Package: clustermq
Title: ZeroMQ-powered cluster jobs
Version: 0.0.2
Author: Michael Schubert <mschu.dev@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Michael Schubert <mschu.dev@gmail.com>
Description: Transparent evaluation of function calls on workers that are
    submitted as LSF jobs without using network-mounted storage
